Project Name: Holtzman (Howard) Collection on Isadora Duncan. Collection 1729
Title: Letter to "Dearest [illegible]", 1907 April 19
Description.note: Reply to letter of "19-4-07", asking for " … assurance by some few words added to the contract --that the orchestra will be able to play the music."
Description.condition: 4 holes punched along left edge.
Format.extent: Holograph letter (signed), 1 leaf (2 pages).
